# =============================================================================
# END OF .gitignore
# =============================================================================
#
# Recommended committed AI context files:
#   .claude/              # Project-level Claude Code configuration
#   .claudeignore         # Patterns Claude Code should ignore (like .gitignore)
#   CLAUDE.md             # Main project instructions (commit this)
#   AGENTS.md             # Additional agent guidance (optional)
#
# Quick start:
#   1. Copy this file to .gitignore in your project root
#   2. Create a .claude/ directory with your rules and skills
#   3. Add CLAUDE.md with project-specific instructions
#   4. Create .claudeignore if you want fine-grained control over what Claude sees
#
# Claude Code will automatically respect both .gitignore and .claudeignore.
# This keeps your repository clean while giving Claude Code the context it needs.
#
# =============================================================================
